History
=======

1.02b -> 1.09b
-       Added xms library, currently xms is only detected, not used.
-       Added a shell around the game boot, enabling multiple startups.

1.01 -> 1.02b
-       Total rewrite of task handling system. Now one player is able
        to run multiple commands synchronously, i.e. in the background.
-       Added the parser defined command '@' to list all running tasks.

1.0 -> 1.01
-       Fixed the delayed execution of verbs of a player when switching
        players before logon.
-       Added cursor command to enable cursor off when having system window.
-       Added restoring of old screen when shutting down driver.
-       Added a protected mode version, still in beta-test phase.
